  {
    "": "strRandomLoop1-0",
    "Fish": "You use your past world's experience well*A natural leader of the group*Though your mutant group is very chaotic",
    "Crystal": "Such a big family*It's inevitable that you join them",
    "Eyes": "With no mouth I am the only one that can see what you want to say*Such lonelyness",
    "Melting": "Your pain will never stop*You do not have long, why do you fight?",
    "Plant": "Such bloodlust you have",
    "YV": "",
    "Steroids": "You see a way out through the void?",
    "Robot": "The factory that made you must be destroyed*However there are many versions*And an infinite amount of parallel copies*An impossible task*An infinite drive for a ruthless machine*",
    "Chicken": "This is not like the movies*but you enjoy the thrill of the fight",
    "Rebel": "I see a path where you do not kill your brother",
    "Hunter": "On the hunt for the next boss*The greatest foes there are*Take them down one by one*And become*The strongers hunter there is",
    "YC": "Family of a God*But not quite a God himself",
    "Sheep": "",
    "Panda": "From the jungle nearly extinct*Yet here you stand one of few",
    "Atom": "Spontanious existence*I can see you slipping through the void at all times",
    "Viking": "Bit by a radioactive serpent*You are one of the luckier ones",
    "Weaponsmith": "The wastelands are a playfield of weaponry*You feel right at home",
    "Angel": "Left your duties for power",
    "Skeleton": "You are not quite like the melting mutant*Instead you are something new*An event so significant it created you as a unique individual",
    "Business Hog": "A stealing thief looking for power and profit*",
    "Horror": "Consumed by radiation*Power fuels more power",
    "Rogue": "",
    "Frog": "Born from the mother*There are many of you, but you are different*You shine gold and sing*Its positivity is almost contagious",
